title: Jan 6th 2.0? Alaska’s KNIFE Politics 08.16.22
itunes:title: Jan 6th 2.0? Alaska’s KNIFE Politics 08.16.22
description:
In episode 1310, Jack and Miles are joined by MC, producer, and streamer Illingsworth to discuss… Jan. 6th 2.0, Will Sarah Palin Replace Alaska’s (Knife-Wielding) Congressman? And more!

  1. Laura Ingraham Says Country Might Be Ready to Move Past Trump: Americans Exhausted By the ‘Constant Battle’
  2. ‘Fox & Friends’ Begs Trump to Make Supporters Lay Off FBI
  3. Rand Paul calls for repeal of Espionage Act after Trump FBI search
  4. Will Sarah Palin Replace Alaska’s (Knife-Wielding) Congressman?
  5. GOP lawmaker once held a knife to Boehner’s throat
  6. Sarah Palin will advance in Alaska's wild House special primary election, CNN projects
  7. Alaska election tests weight of Sarah Palin’s celebrity – and Trump’s sway
  8. 'Another day in paradise. This is a strange day': Trump jokes about FBI raid at Mar-a-Lago while dialing in to 15-minute telephone rally for Sarah Palin's House campaign
  9. Trump bashed Alaska’s ranked choice voting, but Republicans likely need those 2nd votes to win

Check Out: https://illingsworks.bandcamp.com/

LISTEN: El arca de Mima by Mima
